import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';

import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import {
  BsArrowLeftShort, BsFillHouseFill, BsArrowUp, BsArrowLeft,
  BsArrowRight, BsArrowDown, BsArrowCounterclockwise, BsGear,
  BsFillPlayFill, BsFillSkipBackwardFill, BsFillSkipForwardFill
} from 'react-icons/bs'


function App() {

  const onButtonClick = (val) => {
    // console.log(sender.target.value)
    console.log(val.props)
  }
  
  
  return (
    <body>
      <Container>
        <Row className="pt-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button onClick={onButtonClick('hi')} value={'hi'}>
              <BsArrowLeftShort />
            </Button>{' '}
            <Button>
              <BsFillHouseFill />
            </Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="pt-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button>
              <BsArrowUp />
            </Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="pt-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button >
              <BsArrowLeft />
            </Button>{' '}
            <Button>
              OK
            </Button>{' '}
            <Button>
              <BsArrowRight />
            </Button>{' '}
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="pt-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button>
              <BsArrowDown />\
            </Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="pt-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button>
              <BsArrowCounterclockwise />
            </Button>{' '}
            <Button>
              <BsGear />
            </Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className="pt-1">
          <Col className="text-center">
            <Button>
              <BsFillSkipBackwardFill />
            </Button>{' '}
            <Button>
              <BsFillPlayFill />
            </Button>{' '}
            <Button>
              <BsFillSkipForwardFill />
            </Button>
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
    </body>
  );
}

export default App;
